OL,6,FConsumer confidence remains "weak" as
OL,7,FChristmas approaches in a blow to
OL,8,Fretailers amid declining expectations
OL,9,Ffor the wider economy, a survey
OL,10,Fsuggests.
OL,12,FConsumer expectations for their
OL,13,Fpersonal finances over the next three
OL,14,Fmonths improved slightly to minus
OL,15,Fthree in November, up from minus four
OL,16,Flast month, according to the British
OL,17,FRetail Consortium (BRC)-Opinium
OL,18,FConsumer Sentiment Monitor.
