OL,6,FExpectations of personal retail
OL,7,Fspending remained positive, edging up
OL,8,Fa point to positive three, although
OL,9,Fthis was "to be expected" as consumers
OL,10,Fprepared for the festive season, the
OL,11,FBRC said.
OL,13,FWithin this, expectations of spending
OL,14,Fon products other than food remained
OL,15,Flow, though expectations of eating out
OL,16,Fimproved the most out of all
OL,17,Fcategories, as people prepare for
OL,18,FChristmas catch-ups with friends and
OL,19,Frelatives.
