OL,3,CConsumer confidence 'weak' as
OL,4,CChristmas approaches
OL,6,FHowever, confidence in the state of
OL,7,Fthe economy worsened by two points to
OL,8,Fminus 19.
OL,10,FBRC chief executive Helen Dickinson
OL,11,Fsaid: "There was little shift in
OL,12,Fconsumer confidence since the
OL,13,FChancellor's Budget, with many worried
OL,14,Fabout the economy in the lead up to
OL,15,FChristmas.
OL,17,F"While there was a very slight
OL,18,Fimprovement in people's expectations
OL,19,Fof their personal financial situation,
OL,20,Fthis was offset by declining
OL,21,Fexpectations of the wider economy.
