OL,6,F"The last month clearly did little to
OL,7,Fshift the dial for households either
OL,8,Fpositively or negatively, however, the
OL,9,Fsame cannot be said for the retail
OL,10,Findustry.
OL,12,F"With over #7 billion in additional
OL,13,Fcosts in 2025 resulting from the
OL,14,FBudget, retailers will have little
OL,15,Fchoice but to raise prices or reduce
OL,16,Finvestment in jobs and shops."
